<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#000000"><td><font color="#FFFFFF"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">Gollum Smells Of-FENS-ive</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">cmg74</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Marshes, Tentacles, and Goblins, OH MY! Gollum recruits minions, while a large fellowship handles what comes its way</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">STARTING:<br />
<br />
The One Ring-Isildur&#39;s Bane<br />
Frodo Tired Traveller<br />
Eowyn Lady of Rohan<br />
Legolas Greenleaf<br />
<br />
ADVENTURE PATH:<br />
<br />
1 Eastement Gullies (denies Aragorn if you go first)<br />
2 Uruk Camp (exerts Uruks, and gives less twilight)<br />
3 Barrows of Edoras (cycles cards)<br />
4 White Rocks (more twilight if opponent uses mounts)<br />
5 Helm&#39;s Gate (won&#39;t hurt me or necessariy help my opponent)<br />
6 Caves of Aglarond (UNDERGROUND)<br />
7 Cavern Entrance (UNDERGROUND)<br />
8 Wizard&#39;s Vale (doesn&#39;t hurt me and gives me twilight if I&#39;m being choked)<br />
9 Caverns Of Isengard (UNDERGROUND)<br />
<br />
FELLOWSHIP:(38 +2 Starting)<br />
<br />
Companions:<br />
Aragorn-Heir of Elendil x4<br />
Faramir Son of Denethor<br />
Boromir Son of Denethor<br />
Haldir Emissary of the Galadhrim<br />
Gimli Dwarf of the Mountain-Race<br />
Sam Son of Hamfest<br />
<br />
ALLIES:<br />
Elrond Lord of Rivendell x2<br />
Galadriel Lady of Light x3<br />
Celeborn Lord of Lorien<br />
Calaglin Elf of Lorien<br />
Orophin Lorien Bowman<br />
Rumil Elven Protector<br />
Filibert Bolger<br />
